window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The world has learned to fear vampires and forgotten another threat. Before the bloodsuckers rose, the gods had perfected one race of predators.</p> <p>And theyâ€™ve decided to hunt again.</p> <p>Avani was raised in another world, away from the secluded werewolves of Oldcrest, but the Elder Pack was the only place where she could be safe. Until now.</p> <p>In his hundreds of years, Alexius has lived without allegiance, without purpose.</p> <p>But when a wounded, hunted wolf crashes into his life, everything changes.</p>"; 
